  "text": "Cisplatin has also increased the sensitivity of tumour cells to cell lysis induced by cytotoxic T cells, though the mechanism was not elucidated [CITATION_1] . More recently, it was reported that cisplatin activates the Fas-ligand (CD95)-related apoptotic pathway in tumour cells. CD95 is widely expressed on MM cell lines but appears to be dysfunctional [CITATION_2] .",
